# Portfolio Website

## Description
This is my personal portfolio website, designed to showcase my projects, skills, and contact information. The purpose of this project is to refresh my knowledge of **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript** while creating a professional portfolio to support my job applications.

The website is fully responsive, ensuring a seamless experience across devices, and includes interactive elements like project cards and smooth scrolling navigation.

**Live Website:** (https://ethanamessmer.github.io/Portfolio/)

---

## Features
- **Interactive Project Cards**: Clickable cards that display project details.
- **Smooth Scrolling**: Smooth transitions when navigating between sections.
- **Responsive Design**: Optimized for desktop, tablet, and mobile devices.
- **Contact Section**: Easy-to-use contact information for potential employers or collaborators.

---

## Technologies Used
  - HTML5 
  - CSS3 (Flexbox, Grid, Media Queries)
  - JavaScript (DOM Manipulation, Event Handling) (In HTML file)
- **Hosting**: GitHub Pages
- **Version Control**: Git and GitHub


